snippet.title: Disney Mirrorverse Villains Trailer | Disney & Marvel Games Showcase
snippet.description:
Oogie Boogie is seen wrecking havoc until the villain Ursula shows up... as a hero? More villains were also shown in this trailer for the upcoming villains of Disney Mirrorverse coming in October.
